{"tid":523634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港知名女星BIG爆晒線　阮兆祥搞笑：係壽包","createTime":"2018-01-08T17:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T17:17:50.000Z","uid":22675,"like":52,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b0cbd22f44f66b2a678ad2ac8ab08cf59f6882a7","tid":523634,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T17:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180108/photo/bkn-20180108213215367-0108_00862_001_01p.jpg?20180108233641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180108%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180108213215367-0108_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20180108233641&h=909c16dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n01月08日(一) 21:32   <br />\n東網電視<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n王祖藍、李思捷、阮兆祥、羅敏莊與女兒陳禛、王君馨、台灣歌手林沖等晚上在將軍澳電視城為薛家燕、黎小田、曹永廉、湯寶如主持的無綫節目《流行經典50年》錄影。阮兆祥看見以低胸性感晚裝亮的薛家燕笑說：「家燕姐唔係無綫，佢係有線㗎。」王祖藍則笑說：「家燕姐你一個都逼爆鏡頭啦。」 <br />\n<br />\n王祖藍又搞笑地笑對薛家燕唱「叉燒包」，阮兆祥笑說：「點止呀，佢呢個係壽包。不過，家燕姐如果守龍門就唔稱職，因為佢中門大開。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180108/mobile/bkn-20180108213215367-0108_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180108%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180108213215367-0108_00862_001.html&d=u3M%2F3QMwHyjrno6sYRaUCNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=fe33b449\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180108/mobile/bkn-20180108213215367-0108_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b27f987daf66c0eeb398014b33d0823f3f908403","tid":523634,"uid":47674,"like":66,"dislike":5,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T17:58:22.000Z","msg":"壽桃同壽包都唔識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d330a29175a22f86e9f2f3f39d09555afb47b11","tid":523634,"uid":29080,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T18:06:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">哈哈哈哈哈哈</span></span>"},{"pid":"65c01